<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Psammonitocrella kumeyaayi sp. nov., male. A P 3 with detached exp 2 and exp 3 B P 4. Asterisks mark the position of apomorphies represented by the loss of spines or setae. Arrow indicates the absence of the enp. DAS = Distal apical seta; DOS = distal outer seta; IAS = inner apical seta." , "Figure 3. Psammonitocrella kumeyaayi sp. nov., male. A P 1 B P 2. Asterisks mark the position of apomorphies represented by the loss of spines or setae. DAS = Distal apical seta; DOS = distal outer seta." , "Figure 2. Psammonitocrella kumeyaayi sp. nov., male. A 6 th to 10 thA 1 segments B 5 thA 1 segment C 1 st to 5 thA 1 segments D enp 2 of A 2 E A 2 with unarmed enp 2 F md G md with unarmed palp H mx 1 I mx 2 J mxp. Asterisk mark the setae of the 4 thA 1 segment, and the md oral bulge." , "Figure 1. Psammonitocrella kumeyaayi sp. nov., male. A Lateral habitus of male B spermatophore C right P 5 D left P 5 E furca. Arrowheads on (A) and asterisks on (E) mark tube pores. Roman numerals indicate each seta on (E)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/478719" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/478718" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/478717" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/478716" .

